{"tid":1262081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（大神請入）有無人跟過禿鷹個聯合國提名","createTime":"2019-06-27T13:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T01:58:02.000Z","uid":269052,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d887bddb72c6aaf8351f7c66b8da38542edf56","tid":1262081,"uid":269052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:59:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/337255/曾偉雄獲中國政府提名-競聘聯合國駐維也納辦事處總幹事\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F337255%2F%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%89%E9%9B%84%E7%8D%B2%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D-%E7%AB%B6%E8%81%98%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E9%A7%90%E7%B6%AD%E4%B9%9F%E7%B4%8D%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E8%99%95%E7%B8%BD%E5%B9%B9%E4%BA%8B&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=c10c488f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/337255/曾偉雄獲中國政府提名-競聘聯合國駐維也納辦事處總幹事</a><br />\n<br />\n如果有人做左就當我無問過<br />\n宜家支那提名左禿鷹做聯合國駐維也納辦事處總幹事<br />\n正常呢 哩種高層聘任要經Security Council<br />\n而五個Permanent Members都不提反對<br />\n包括 中 英 美 法 俄<br />\n中俄可以唔使理<br />\n<br />\n有無大神可以send信去英 法 美 反對聘任禿鷹<br />\n<br />\n一係 雨傘同612新仇大恨 畀前一哥做到聯合國要職 黑警實好得戚<br />\n二係 中國提名得 落習敗敗面就岩 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要畀習敗敗知 宜家佢因為面子唔肯讓步 香港就要落佢更大既面</span></span>"},{"pid":"fe4c1eb19d889f944234a7b6fec3c3826a1cff1d","tid":1262081,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:01:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"556d8fffe9f72cc03ad02b854c41db1a02e067aa","tid":1262081,"uid":50196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:06:12.000Z","msg":"又要召喚攬炒巴"},{"pid":"1e88323b319e85d1aed20e3f6660d07265d0766a","tid":1262081,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:07:04.000Z","msg":"推到攪炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im